text: You know they say the world is safer than has ever been in history of civilization
do you can feel safer today than you did yesterday?
I know I don't.
The world has changed the war were fighting today...
needs a different kind of soldier.
We need people with the skills
and the attitude
to take on threats we don't even know exist.
We need someone who can walk into a tornado,
and come out the other side like it was a damned gentle breeze.
"If you wanted me back...
you could've just asked me."
Let me simplify it for you.
Kick some ass,
and try to look dope while you're doing it.
I could definitely make that work!

girls,
global domination,
